{"tid":2086901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tommy 收到死亡恐嚇信 話聽日見到就會 車斤 佢","createTime":"2020-06-30T13:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:08:16.000Z","uid":22556,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7bab9d50ed11794a3089e9dfc79548529499c0","tid":2086901,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URAvD3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURAvD3M.jpg&h=10e47ccc&s={SIZE}\" />DLLMCH，今日咩事！！！<br />\n<br />\n啱啱同Eva分開左唔夠5分鐘，我要去做野，佢就返屋企！<br />\n<br />\n佢差唔多去到屋企樓下商場，有個男人好大力推左佢一下，大陸口音，之後叫佢俾呢紙我！嚇到佢喊咁濟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩今日無帶小朋友，唔係後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街，你班藍絲狗要搞就下次見L到我，唔好淨係拍我，真係郁手打9我！依家去嚇個女人做乜L！！！<br />\n<br />\n我DLGH！首先我會加强保安，保護好家人先！<br />\n<br />\n然後狗我就唔會報㗎啦，因為報嚟係把L！但係聽日SOGO我就一定去！<br />\n<br />\n藍絲狗，記L得見到我要斬我呀！我未驚過呀！柒頭！！！<br />\n<br />\n手足，聽日2點，SOGO見！<br />\n<br />\nSorr，講野1999，未冷靜到！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/3210722718988340/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F802472909813345%2Fposts%2F3210722718988340%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=db5ea4be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/802472909813345/posts/3210722718988340/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c1210c236a0d8622e56dd7fbb4ad08d7a0ee90e9","tid":2086901,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:04:26.000Z","msg":"大陸佬落黎香港搞屎搞棍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43dea74027c7bf7e1a004747fad170429aca82f","tid":2086901,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"